1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,320
Después del curro...

2
00:00:01,320 --> 00:00:02,520
me subo
a la bici.

3
00:00:02,520 --> 00:00:03,440
Sin plan.

4
00:00:03,440 --> 00:00:04,880
Solo yo,
las calles...

5
00:00:04,880 --> 00:00:06,040
y el aire
en la cara.

6
00:00:06,040 --> 00:00:07,040
Y es que mola.

7
00:00:07,040 --> 00:00:07,880
Mola mucho.

8
00:00:07,880 --> 00:00:09,000
Pedalear
por tu ciudad,

9
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:09,840
ver el barrio,

10
00:00:09,840 --> 00:00:10,800
desconectar
de todo.

11
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:11,600
Para mí
es lo mejor

12
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:12,360
que puedo hacer

13
00:00:12,360 --> 00:00:13,640
después de
un día largo.

14
00:00:13,640 --> 00:00:14,400
Y a veces
de paso

15
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:15,400
pillo cosas
en la calle

16
00:00:15,400 --> 00:00:16,320
que aún sirven

17
00:00:16,320 --> 00:00:17,000
y las comparto.

18
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:18,120
Que alguien
las aproveche,

19
00:00:18,120 --> 00:00:18,440
¿no?

20
00:00:18,440 --> 00:00:18,760
Y mira,

21
00:00:18,760 --> 00:00:19,960
resulta que hay
bastante gente

22
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:21,080
haciendo lo mismo.

23
00:00:21,080 --> 00:00:22,000
En bici,
andando,

24
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:22,680
como sea.

25
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:23,560
Buena gente.

26
00:00:23,560 --> 00:00:24,600
Si os mola
la idea...

27
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:25,280
hay sitio.

